profile_positions.description:
Matsutani Europe B.V. is the Dutch branch of Matsutani Chemical Industry Co., Ltd., Japan's leading producer of specialty food starches and maltodextrins. It is engaged in the manufacture, development and sale of modified starch and dietary fiber and other specific health foods that contain these ingredients.

Responsibilities: 
*Coordinate sales and research activities between the Asian headquarters and the distributors of the local European representative office (in Japanese, English and Dutch); 
*Perform B2B sales activities such as following up on leads, preparing promotion material, prepare sales reports on account status
*Support the daily business activities of the local office; 
*Perform general administrative tasks: such as filing order sheets and invoices, managing calendar and answering phone calls; 
*Input sales figures, its data analysis and inventory control.
